        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Mamie Till-Mobley Memorial Stamp Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the U.S. Postal Service to issue a commemorative postage stamp in honor of Mamie Till-Mobley, the mother of Emmett Till (who was kidnapped and lynched in 1955).</p>]]>
        </text>
